  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install dmz-cursor-theme by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>cd DMZ-White/pngs &amp;&amp;
./make.sh &amp;&amp;
cd - &amp;&amp;
cd DMZ-Black/pngs &amp;&amp;
./make.sh &amp;&amp;
cd -</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>mkdir -pv /usr/share/icons/DMZ-White/cursors &amp;&amp;
mkdir -pv /usr/share/icons/DMZ-Black/cursors &amp;&amp;
cp -v DMZ-White/*.theme /usr/share/icons/DMZ-White &amp;&amp;
cp -v DMZ-White/xcursors/* /usr/share/icons/DMZ-White/cursors &amp;&amp;
cp -v DMZ-Black/*.theme /usr/share/icons/DMZ-Black &amp;&amp;
cp -v DMZ-Black/xcursors/* /usr/share/icons/DMZ-Black/cursors</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

